      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1910_AS_RBH_2_00022"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168815">Wien XVIII. Sternwartestrasse 71</rs></hi></addrLine></address><address><addrLine><pb facs="1910_AS_RBH_2_00021"/>Herr <hi rend="latintype">Dr. Richard
                     Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb68">Wien XVIII</rs></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb235251">Hasenauerstr 59</rs></hi>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><pb facs="1910_AS_RBH_2_00023"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><date when="1910-11-22">22. 11 910</date>.</seg></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168815">Wien XVIII. Sternwartestrasse 71</rs></hi></seg></opener><p>Die einzige <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01984-1"/>Er<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>te Stock Loge<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01984-1">für die <rs type="event" ref="#pmb35254" subtype="implied">Uraufführung</rs> von <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29937">Der junge Medardus</rs> am <ref target="1910-11-24" type="schnitzler-tagebuch" subtype="date-only"/> im <rs type="place" ref="#pmb14">Burgtheater</rs></note> außer der für meinen <rs type="person" ref="#pmb12698">Bruder</rs>! In der
               Hoffnung einer guten <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01984-2"/><rs type="work" ref="#pmb52544" subtype="implied">Parodie</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01984-2">Anspielung auf <rs type="work" ref="#pmb52544">Das Echo des Lebens</rs>, das nach der Generalprobe
                  von <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29905">Der Ruf des Lebens</rs> am <ref target="1909-12-10" subtype="date-only" type="schnitzler-tagebuch"/> verfasst
                  wurde.</note></p><closer>Ihr <signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
